msgid "<SmallInline url='/img/icons/logo-thunderbird.png'/> Configure Thunderbird Desktop (on a desktop computer)"
msgstr "<SmallInline url='/img/icons/logo-thunderbird.png'/> Thunderbird Desktop konfigurieren (auf einem Desktop-Computer)"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/35.email/05.clients.mdx:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "To manually configure a new account in Thunderbird Desktop, add the account information, then click on 'Configure manually'.\n"
msgstr "Um ein neues Konto in Thunderbird Desktop manuell zu konfigurieren, fügen Sie die Kontoinformationen hinzu und wählen:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/35.email/05.clients.mdx:33
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"- For the incoming server, use IMAP with port 993 and SSL/TLS.\n"
"- For outgoing server, use port 587 with STARTTLS. \n"
"- Select 'Normal Password' for the the authentication method of both. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/35.email/05.clients.mdx:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "You may need to accept the certificate exceptions for fetching mails and after you send your first mail. Don't forget to remove the dot before the domain name.\n"
msgstr "Möglicherweise müssen Sie die Zertifikatsausnahmen für das Abrufen von E-Mails und nach dem Senden Ihrer ersten E-Mail akzeptieren. Vergessen Sie nicht, den Punkt vor dem Domainnamen zu entfernen.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/35.email/05.clients.mdx:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "- [Manage alias mails](https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/configuring-email-aliases)\n"
msgstr "- [Alias-Mails verwalten](https://support.mozilla.org/de/kb/configuring-email-aliases)\n"

